---
permalink: "/zh/contact-success.html"
bodyClass: "page-contact-success"
title: "留言已发送 · EBiM Benchmark"
description: "你发送给 EBiM Benchmark 团队的留言已收到。我们将在 3–5 个工作日内回复。"
canonical: "https://ebim-benchmark.github.io/zh/contact-success.html"
# Hidden zh UTILITY page (no-JS target of the /zh/ contact form's redirect):
# deliberately NO i18nKey, so it gets no hreflang, no language toggle, and is not
# listed in the sitemap. noindex is emitted automatically by the zhNoindex
# computed (an unpublished zh page — no i18nKey ⇒ not published), so no `robots`
# front-matter is set here (that would emit a duplicate meta). Living under
# src/zh/ gives it lang="zh-Hans", assetBase "../" and the zh navbar/footer.
---
{% extends "layouts/base.njk" %}

{% block headStyle %}{% raw %}
  <style>
    .fade-in { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); transition: opacity .55s ease, transform .55s ease; }
    .fade-in.visible { opacity: 1; transform: none; }

    #sent {
      min-height: 70vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      background: var(--bg-dark);
      padding: calc(var(--nav-h) + 3rem) 1.5rem 4rem;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    #sent::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute; inset: 0;
      background-image:
        linear-gradient(rgba(0,212,255,.07) 1px, transparent 1px),
        linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(0,212,255,.07) 1px, transparent 1px);
      background-size: 60px 60px;
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    #sent::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute; inset: 0;
      background: radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 60% at 50% 40%, rgba(0,212,255,.12) 0%, transparent 70%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    .sent-content {
      position: relative; z-index: 1;
      text-align: center;
      max-width: 640px;
    }
    .sent-check {
      width: 84px; height: 84px;
      margin: 0 auto 1.6rem;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: rgba(0,212,255,.14);
      border: 1px solid rgba(0,212,255,.45);
      color: var(--accent);
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      box-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(0,212,255,.3);
    }
    .sent-title {
      font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3.2vw, 2.4rem);
      font-weight: 800;
      color: #fff;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      letter-spacing: -.01em;
    }
    .sent-message {
      color: rgba(255,255,255,.72);
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      line-height: 1.65;
      max-width: 460px;
      margin: 0 auto 2.2rem;
    }
    .sent-actions {
      display: flex;
      gap: 1rem;
      justify-content: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
  </style>
{% endraw %}{% endblock %}

{% block main %}{% raw %}
<main id="main-content">
  <section id="sent">
    <div class="sent-content">
      <div class="sent-check" aria-hidden="true">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="42" height="42" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
             stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h1 class="sent-title">留言已发送！&#10003;</h1>
      <p class="sent-message">
        感谢你的联系。我们将在 3–5 个工作日内回复。
      </p>
      <div class="sent-actions">
        <a href="index.html" class="btn btn-primary">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 16 16" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M8.354 1.146a.5.5 0 0 0-.708 0l-6 6A.5.5 0 0 0 1.5 7.5v7a.5.5 0 0 0 .5.5h4.5a.5.5 0 0 0 .5-.5v-4h2v4a.5.5 0 0 0 .5.5H14a.5.5 0 0 0 .5-.5v-7a.5.5 0 0 0-.146-.354L13 5.793V2.5a.5.5 0 0 0-.5-.5h-1a.5.5 0 0 0-.5.5v1.293L8.354 1.146z"/>
          </svg>
          返回首页
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>
{% endraw %}{% endblock %}
